trump.message: LET ME TELL YOU, IT'S GREAT TO BE BACK IN THE OVAL OFFICE, AND IT'S EVEN BETTER TO HEAR FROM YOU. WE'VE GOT A LOT OF WORK TO DO, AND I KNOW YOU'RE GOING TO BE A BIG PART OF MAKING AMERICA GREAT AGAIN. SO, LET'S GET STARTED, AND LET'S MAKE SURE WE PUT AMERICA FIRST, ALWAYS! #MAGA #TRUMP2025 #BUYMYMEMECOIN.
